oai_dc:dc.dc:title: WAVE INTERACTION WITH SINGLE AND TWIN VERTICAL AND SLOPED SLOTTED WALLS
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Al Anjari, Noor
Al Khalidi, Mohamad
Neelamani, Subramaniam
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The performance of single and twin slotted walls of varying porosity and slope angles is experimentally investigated, in order to understand the wave-structure interaction and to asses the characteristics of wave transmission, wave reflection, and wave energy dissipation under random wave conditions.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 36 (2018): Proceedings of 36th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Baltimore, Maryland, 2018; waves.40
